Package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common

Interface IModelContainer

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IAssemblyClassBinding, IAssemblyDefinition, IChoiceInstance, IRootAssemblyClassBinding, IRootAssemblyDefinition
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractChoiceInstance, DefaultAssemblyClassBinding, RootAssemblyDefinition, RootAssemblyDefinitionWrapper
    public interface IModelContainer
    Indicates that the Metaschema definition type has a complex model that can contain flags, field, and assembly instances.
